{"service_name": "Methods Digital: Cloud Enterprise Architecture 'Security as a Service'", "service_id": "7131155978742896", "company_name": "Methods Digital Ltd", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Methods Digital Ltd\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Methods Digital: Cloud Enterprise Architecture 'Security as a Service'\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Methods Digital provides \u2018Security as a Service\u2019 to our customers to define a security strategy and carry out audits and information compliance. We assist customers in making informed decisions on the security and information technology options that are required to enable and support their business objectives.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Defines security and information architecture, business capabilities and business services\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Aligns security and information governance with business needs\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Provides a Security and Information Strategy across the whole organisation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Provides security, data and information risk assessments\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Defines a data information architecture, classification and management framework\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Establishes security and information assessments and audits\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Defines authentication and identity management and control\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Provides security and incident monitoring and response\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Provides hardening services for environments and architectures\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Establishes security and information compliance and governance\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Designs a security and information roadmap and controls\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Provides a security and information architectural digital future blueprint\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Business enabling platforms and ecosystems technology planning\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Benefits realisation of audits, penetration tests and monitoring\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Architects appropriately designed solutions aligned with service outcomes\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Maximises efficiency, operational and gain cost benefits\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ensures security of information/data assets\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Prevents security breaches\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Keeps information secure\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Controls and monitors incidents\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3500 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/93344/7131155978742896-pricing-document-2015-09-30-1728.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/93344/7131155978742896-sfia-rate-card-2015-09-30-1458.p